  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>\"I never dreamed that keeping an inn could be so dangerous.\" — <a href=\"/index.php/Hyle_Hunt\" title=\"Hyle Hunt\"> Ser Hyle</a> <br />\"It is being common-born that is dangerous, when the great lords play their <b>game of thrones.</b> Isn't that so, Dog?\" — <a href=\"/index.php/Meribald\" title=\"Meribald\"> Septon Meribald</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_37\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 37\">Chapter 37</a>, Brienne VII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404060237\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.009 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 70/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 312/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 527/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    4.280      1 -total\n100.00%    4.280      1 Template:Ref\n 58.18%    2.490      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:29776-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404060237 and revision id 276637\n -->\n",
